menghubungimu nanti!

592
00:53:51,540 --> 00:53:52,570
Selamat bekerja!

593
00:53:52,570 --> 00:53:53,650
Aku mencintaimu.

594
00:53:58,780 --> 00:54:01,330
Pria itu melihat wajahku.

595
00:54:02,380 --> 00:54:04,260
Apa kau tertangkap?

596
00:54:04,260 --> 00:54:06,310
Bukan seperti itu, tapi...

597
00:54:06,310 --> 00:54:10,030
